    <note>Yan(3) Zao [22725] I assume that he was the first lineage patriarch of documented distinction of the Longqi Yan(3). His 6th generation descendant, Zhi [22730], has the same generational name as Yizhong's [22736] (q.v.) great grandfather, Shi [22728], although the generations have become chronologically distant by this time. Therefore, I make him lineage kin of a previous generation for Xikong [22726] and his brother, Xizhe [22727], and 6th generation ancestor of Shi. Zao was an associate of Cai(1) Xiang. Renming Da cidian, p. 1731.</note>
